## Verification Checklist

- [ ] `setCommitStatus()` calls `octokit.repos.createCommitStatus()` with correct parameters
- [ ] Default context is `gblockparty/preview`
- [ ] Default descriptions provided for each state
- [ ] `target_url` passed through when provided (for success state)
- [ ] Description truncated to 140 characters
- [ ] Errors are caught and logged (not thrown)
- [ ] Function logs the operation at info level (with short SHA for readability)
- [ ] Function logs errors at error level with full error context
- [ ] Works with installation-scoped Octokit (not user token)

